john randolph " jack " webb ( april 2 , 1920   – december 23 , 1982 ) , also known by the pen name john randolph , was an american actor , television producer , director , and screenwriter , who is most famous for his role as sergeant joe friday in the radio and television series , dragnet .

it 's the police : the title of this jack webb tv drama refers to a systematic police search for a criminal

